Imports:
Suggests:
Description: PCIC's suite of routines for downscaling coarse
    scale global climate model (GCM) output to a fine spatial
    resolution. Includes Bias-Corrected Spatial Downscaling (BCDS),
    Bias-Correction Constructed Analogues (BCCA), Bias Correction/Climate
    Imprint (BCCI), and Bias Correction/Constructed Analogues with
    Quantilemapping reordering (BCCAQ).
